H3.text: One of the longest ruling monarchs of the 20th century and a massive and dangerous volcano in the USA share which name. Rainier

A4.text: Mount Rainier is a large active stratovolcano in the Cascade Range of the Pacific Northwest in the United States.

A5.text: George Vancouver named Mount Rainier in honor of his friend, Rear Admiral Peter Rainier.
